	ts Water’s Table restaurant. See the Easter Bunny and waterfront views whi
	le enjoying breakfast favorites ranging from bacon to crisp breakfast pota
	toes and other assorted foods. With special dining options for kids such a
	s chicken tenders\, as well as a dessert spread for all\, you can create y
	our perfect meal.\n\nThe holiday brunch is $75 for adults\, $25 for childr
	en between the ages of five and twelve\, and complimentary for children fo
